# Multi-dimensional contact intelligence system
# This app uses multiple scraping methods in parallel to find real contact info:
# - Playwright headless browser (Google, Bing, DuckDuckGo)
# - CORS proxy scraping (AllOrigins, ThingProxy, corsproxy.io)
# - Direct source scraping (LinkedIn, Crunchbase, SAM.gov, company websites)
# - Optional search APIs (Serper, SerpAPI, Google Custom Search)
#
# The app works WITHOUT API keys using scraping methods.
# Add API keys below to boost search capabilities and avoid rate limits.

# Optional: Serper API (2,000 free searches/month)
# Get key at: https://serper.dev/api-key
# SERPER_API_KEY=your_serper_key_here

# Optional: SerpAPI (100 free searches/month)
# Get key at: https://serpapi.com/users/sign_up
# SERPAPI_KEY=your_serpapi_key_here

# Optional: Google Custom Search API (100 free searches/day)
# Get key at: https://developers.google.com/custom-search/v1/overview
# GOOGLE_API_KEY=your_google_api_key_here
# GOOGLE_CX=your_google_search_engine_id_here
